                BBB Rating Scorecard
            






Overview


Sun Life Assurance Company (US) is a wholly-owned subsidiary of Sun Life Financial, Inc. located and incorporated in Canada in 1871 . Sun Life Assurance Company  offers  insurance products to individuals and businesses, including group and individual life insurance, and group disability and medical stop-loss insurance. The  Wellesley Hills, Massachusetts office handles items for policies issued in the United States only.



