Company Overview of Sun Life Assurance Company Of Canada



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Sun Life Assurance Company of Canada, a diversified financial services company, provides savings, retirement and pension, and insurance products to individuals and groups in Canada, the United States, the United Kingdom, and Asia. It operates through Sun Life Financial Canada, SLF U.S., and Sun Life Financial Asia segments. The company offers various insurance products, such as health, life, travel, car and home, mortgage protection, family, and workplace health and benefit insurance, as well as insurance solutions to associations and affinity groups, banks and credit unions, and educational institutions or organizations. It also provides investment products and solutions, such as savings, r...
Sun Life Assurance Company of Canada, a diversified financial services company, provides savings, retirement and pension, and insurance products to individuals and groups in Canada, the United States, the United Kingdom, and Asia. It operates through Sun Life Financial Canada, SLF U.S., and Sun Life Financial Asia segments. The company offers various insurance products, such as health, life, travel, car and home, mortgage protection, family, and workplace health and benefit insurance, as well as insurance solutions to associations and affinity groups, banks and credit unions, and educational institutions or organizations. It also provides investment products and solutions, such as savings, retirement income, guaranteed interest products, annuity products, mutual funds, segregated funds, and workplace pensions and savings; registered retirement savings plans, tax-free savings accounts, and registered education savings plans; and registered retirement income funds and life income funds. The company is headquartered in Toronto, Canada. Sun Life Assurance Company of Canada is a subsidiary of Sun Life Financial Inc.
Detailed Description


