Sun Life Assurance Company Of Canada Key Developments

The Toronto Raptors and Sun Life Assurance Company of Canada Expands the Long-Standing Partnership
Jul 6 17
The Toronto Raptors and Sun Life Assurance Company of Canada have expanded their long-standing partnership to feature a prominent program in support of diabetes awareness and prevention, and beginning in the 2017-18 season, include the first jersey patch partnership in the team's history.


